  "remarks": "\nAndrey PATRUSHEV (hereafter PATRUSHEV) is a senior figure in the Russian energy industry and is a former member of the Management Board and Deputy General Director of Gazprom Neft\n, \na subsidiary of Russian energy corporation Gazprom\n. In this role \nPATRUSHEV is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or equivalent in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia – the energy sector.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
